message:
can't build and application in flash builder 4.6 and getting this error
any help will be apreciated

data.message:
It seems the error happen when "importing" a project, not building it.
If you're sure the project you're importing doesn't have any problem, try repairing the installation of Flash Builder.
Also, make sure to disable UAC or run Flash Builder as Administrator.

Friendly advise, if you can, don't use Flash :)
